(57, '21', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'I want to enhance employee wellness this year — where do I start?', 'Enhancing employee wellness is a great goal to have for your organization. Here are some steps you can take to get started:\n\n1. Conduct a wellness assessment: Before implementing any wellness initiatives, it\'s important to understand the current wellness needs and challenges of your employees. You can do this through surveys, focus groups, or interviews to gather feedback on their wellness preferences and concerns.\n\n2. Create a wellness program: Based on the results of the assessment, develop a wellness program that addresses the specific needs and interests of your employees. This could include initiatives such as fitness challenges, nutrition education, mental health resources, stress management workshops, and incentives for healthy behaviors.\n\n3. Provide resources and support: Make sure employees have access to the resources and support they need to participate in the wellness program. This could include providing healthy snacks in the office, offering wellness workshops or seminars', 0, 0, '2025-04-22 14:49:16'),
(58, '4', '[{\"question_id\":\"30\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"31\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"32\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"33\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '5', '8', 'how to grow my business by 20%', '1. Evaluate your current business operations and identify areas for growth. This could include expanding your product or service offerings, entering new markets, or improving your marketing and sales strategies.\n\n2. Set specific and achievable goals for your business growth, such as increasing sales revenue, acquiring new customers, or expanding your online presence.\n\n3. Develop a detailed business plan outlining the steps you need to take to achieve your growth goals. This plan should include timelines, milestones, and resources needed to support your growth strategy.\n\n4. Invest in marketing and advertising efforts to reach a larger audience and attract new customers. This could include social media marketing, email campaigns, SEO, and online advertising.\n\n5. Consider expanding your business through partnerships, collaborations, or strategic alliances with other companies or organizations in your industry.\n\n6. Focus on improving customer satisfaction and retention to increase repeat b', 0, 0, '2025-04-22 19:05:19'),
