(75, '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'need expense projection for upcoming month of my company ?', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal with me regarding the expense projection for the upcoming month of your company.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nI will start by gathering all relevant information and insights related to your company\'s expenses.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nYour goal is to have an expense projection for the upcoming month to better manage your company\'s finances.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \nTo assess this goal, we will evaluate the impact of having an accurate expense projection, the feasibility of obtaining the necessary data, and its alignment with your company\'s overall financial objectives.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nWe will create a strategy map that outlines the decision paths required to gather the necessary information and create the expense projection.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nWe will run scenario simulations based on different expense variables and factors to ensure the projection is as accurate as possible.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- CEO: To have a clear expense projection for the upcoming month to make informed financial decisions.\n- CFO: To analyze and validate the expense data for accuracy and reliability.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \nComplementary goals may include optimizing expenses, identifying cost-saving opportunities, and improving financial forecasting processes.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nThe final outcome will be a detailed expense projection for the upcoming month that will support your company in making sound financial decisions.', 0, 0, '2025-04-25 05:20:13'),
(78, '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"40\",\"answer\":\"Expand outreach to underrepresented communities, anonymized screening for select roles, and ERG-driven awareness.\"},{\"question_id\":\"41\",\"answer\":\"Inclusion is tracked through engagement pulse surveys and quarterly review of inclusive behaviors across leadership levels.\"},{\"question_id\":\"42\",\"answer\":\"Use of structured rubrics, bias interrupter prompts during interviews, and training for hiring panels.\"},{\"question_id\":\"43\",\"answer\":\"It\'s a foundational pillar \\u2014 our culture and innovation strategy both rely on a diverse, inclusive workforce.\"}]', '6', '6', '8', '11', 'We want to increase employee participation in learning programs by 30%', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal with us. We appreciate your focus on increasing employee participation in learning programs.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nTo better understand your objective, could you please provide insights on your current employee learning programs and the factors affecting participation rates?\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nYour goal is to increase employee participation in learning programs by 30%.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \nImpact: Increasing employee participation can lead to enhanced skills and job satisfaction.\nFeasibility: Depending on current participation rates, achieving a 30% increase may require implementing effective strategies.\nAlignment: This goal aligns with the organization\'s focus on continuous employee development.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nPossible decision paths could include enhancing program content, promoting learning opportunities, and offering incentives for participation.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nSimulations could explore the potential impact of different strategies on employee engagement and overall performance.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- HR Manager: Develop strategies to increase employee participation in learning programs by 30%.\n- Learning & Development Specialist: Enhance program content to boost employee engagement.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \nA complementary goal could focus on measuring the effectiveness of the learning programs in improving employee performance.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nBy increasing employee participation in learning programs by 30%, your organization can foster a culture of continuous learning and development.', 0, 0, '2025-04-25 15:30:22'),
(79, '20', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, 0, '2025-04-25 15:48:01'),
(80, '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'We need to improve lead conversion rates from our digital ads.', '🧩 Step 1: Thank you for sharing your goal to improve lead conversion rates from your digital ads.\n\n📁 Step 2: It\'s important to document that increasing lead conversion rates is a critical aspect of your marketing strategy.\n\n📊 Step 3: In assessing this goal, it is evident that enhancing lead conversion rates can lead to higher ROI and improved overall performance in your digital advertising efforts.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring - Impact: High, Feasibility: Moderate, Alignment: High\n\n🗺️ Step 5: By mapping out decision paths, we can explore strategies such as optimizing ad performance, refining targeting methods, and improving landing page design to increase lead conversion rates.\n\n🔮 Step 6: In scenario simulations, we can test different variables and analyze their impact on lead conversion rates to determine the most effective strategies.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role:\n- Marketing Team: Increase lead conversion rates by refining digital ad strategies.\n- Design Team: Enhance landing page design to improve user experience and drive conversions.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals:\n- Implementing A/B testing to optimize ad performance.\n- Utilizing retargeting strategies to re-engage potential leads.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary: By strategically focusing on improving lead conversion rates from digital ads, we aim to drive enhanced performance, increased ROI, and overall success in your marketing efforts.', 0, 0, '2025-04-25 15:48:24'),
