(86, '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'Our goal this year is to increase brand awareness in North America. Can you help me assess this and guide the team?', '🧩 **Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement**\nAbsolutely, I can assist you with assessing and guiding the team to increase brand awareness in North America this year.\n\n📁 **Step 2: Document Insights**\nTo begin, let\'s gather insights on your current brand awareness strategies in North America and any previous efforts.\n\n📊 **Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary**\nIncreasing brand awareness in North America is a crucial objective for your team this year.\n\n📈 **Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)**\nWe will evaluate the impact, feasibility, and alignment of this goal to ensure its success.\n\n🗺️ **Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)**\nWe will create decision paths to determine the most effective strategies for expanding brand awareness in North America.\n\n🔮 **Step 6: Scenario Simulations**\nWe will also run scenario simulations to anticipate potential outcomes and adjust strategies accordingly.\n\n👥 **Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role**\nFor the marketing team, the goal is to implement targeted campaigns to increase brand visibility in North America.\n\n📌 **Complementary Goals (if applicable)**\nComplementary goals may include enhancing customer engagement and driving conversions in tandem with brand awareness efforts.\n\n✅ **Final Outcome Summary**\nThe final outcome will be a strategic roadmap to elevate brand awareness in North America this year. Let\'s get started on achieving this goal!', 0, 0, '2025-05-02 11:44:16'),
