(90, '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"44\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"45\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"46\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"47\",\"answer\":\"text\"}]', '6', '6', '9', '12', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year. GOALSYNC - GPT INSTRUCTION SET For Standardized Output Generation (1) 1.docx', '🧩 Step 1: Thank you for sharing your goal of reducing voluntary turnover in your sales team this year.\n\n📁 Step 2: Based on your goal, it is important to document insights regarding the current turnover rates, reasons for voluntary turnover, employee feedback, and historical data on turnover trends.\n\n📊 Step 3: The goal assessment summary is focused on reducing voluntary turnover within the sales team to improve employee retention and overall team stability.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring your goal based on Impact, Feasibility, and Alignment is crucial for strategic planning. This will help determine the potential impact of reducing turnover, feasibility of implementing changes, and alignment with organizational objectives.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Developing a strategy map with decision paths will involve analyzing potential interventions, such as improving retention strategies, addressing employee concerns, and enhancing the overall sales team environment.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Through scenario simulations, we can explore different outcomes based on various strategies to reduce turnover, identifying potential obstacles and solutions to achieve your goal effectively.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased goal by role: \"As the sales team leader, I aim to implement effective retention strategies to decrease voluntary turnover within the sales team this year.\"\n\n📌 Complementary Goals: Enhancing employee engagement, improving communication within the sales team, and strengthening leadership development programs may support the main goal of reducing turnover.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary: By employing a strategic approach focused on retention strategies and employee satisfaction, we aim to reduce voluntary turnover in the sales team, leading to improved team performance and overall business success.', 0, 0, '2025-05-02 13:54:44'),
