(93, '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'I need a 20% increase in my sales .', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement\nThank you for sharing your goal of needing a 20% increase in your sales.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights\nDocumenting the goal of a 20% sales increase for reference.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary\nThe goal is clear - a 20% increase in sales.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)\nImpact: Achieving a 20% increase in sales would significantly boost revenue.\nFeasibility: Feasibility depends on current market conditions and sales strategies.\nAlignment: Sales increase aligns with business growth objectives.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)\nStrategy options may include optimizing marketing campaigns, expanding reach to new markets, or improving sales team performance.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations\nSimulating scenarios based on different strategies to achieve a 20% sales increase.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role\n- Sales Manager: Increase sales by 20% through strategic initiatives.\n- Marketing Team: Support sales growth with targeted campaigns.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)\nComplementary goals may focus on improving customer retention or enhancing product offerings.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary\nThe final outcome will be a comprehensive strategy to achieve your goal of a 20% increase in sales.', 0, 0, '2025-05-07 06:12:41'),
(94, '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'I need a 20% increase in my sales .', '✅ Final Outcome Summary  \n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nAcknowledging the user\'s goal of a 20% increase in sales. Do you need to scan any documents for this goal?\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nNo documents found, relying on discussed information.  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nAssessing the complexity, resource requirements, and strategic alignment of the sales increase goal.  \n- Complexity: Moderate  \n- Resource Requirements: Medium  \n- Strategic Alignment: High  \n- Assign Aggressiveness: Moderate  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: 8/10  \n- Feasibility: 7/10  \n- Alignment: 9/10  \n- Total Score: 24/30  \n- Interpretation: High potential impact, moderate feasibility, strong strategic alignment but requires significant effort.  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \nPresenting 3-4 named paths with descriptions, estimated effort, risk, and ROI potential.  \nRecommendation: Focus on high-value customer retention for steady growth.  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nSimulating 2 options (A & B) with timelines, metrics, and risk levels.  \nRecommendation: Option B - Introduce targeted marketing campaigns for existing customer base.  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- Sales Manager: Increase repeat sales by developing loyalty programs.  \n- Marketing Director: Improve customer acquisition strategies to support sales growth.  \n- Financial Analyst: Monitor ROI of implemented marketing initiatives.  \n\n📌 Complementary Goals  \nSuggesting a synergistic sub-goal of improving customer satisfaction to strengthen loyalty programs.  \nSynergy Level: Strong  \n\nNext Step: Implement targeted marketing campaigns for existing customer base to increase sales.', 0, 0, '2025-05-07 06:19:32'),
(95, '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"44\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"45\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"46\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"47\",\"answer\":\"text\"}]', '6', '6', '9', '12', 'I need a 20% increase in my sales', '✅ Final Outcome Summary:\n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \n- Acknowledge the user’s goal of a 20% increase in sales. Ask if document scan is needed.  \n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \n- No documents provided.  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \n- Complexity: Moderate  \n- Resource Requirements: High  \n- Strategic Alignment: Strong  \n- Aggressiveness: Aggressive  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: 8/10  \n- Feasibility: 7/10  \n- Alignment: 9/10  \n- Total Score: 24/30  \n- Interpretation: Strong potential for growth, but resource-intensive.  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \n- Path 1: Launch targeted marketing campaign – Effort: High, Risk: Moderate, ROI Potential: High  \n- Path 2: Expand distribution channels – Effort: Moderate, Risk: Low, ROI Potential: Moderate  \n- Path 3: Improve sales team training – Effort: High, Risk: Low, ROI Potential: Moderate  \n- Recommended: Launch targeted marketing campaign  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \n- Option A: Launch targeted marketing campaign – 6 months, 15% increase in sales, Medium risk  \n- Option B: Expand distribution channels – 8 months, 10% increase in sales, Low risk  \n- Recommended: Option A  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- Sales Manager: Increase customer outreach efforts by 30%  \n- Marketing Director: Develop a targeted marketing campaign to attract new customers  \n- Operations Manager: Streamline order fulfillment process for increased efficiency  \n\n📌 Complementary Goals  \n- Implement customer loyalty program to increase repeat business  \n- Synergy level: Strong  \n\nNext Step: Initiate the targeted marketing campaign and monitor progress closely.', 0, 0, '2025-05-07 06:27:54'),
(96, '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'irror executive tone: Clear, strategic, concise. Use emojis for section headers.', '🔍 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal with us. Do you require a document scan to proceed?\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nNo documents were found based on our search.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \n- Complexity: Easy\n- Resource Requirements: Low\n- Strategic Alignment: Moderate\n- Aggressiveness: Aggressive\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: 7/10\n- Feasibility: 8/10\n- Alignment: 6/10\n- Total Score: 21/30\n- Strengths: Low resource requirements, high impact potential\n- Risks: Limited alignment with strategic goals\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \n- Option 1: Quick Implementation (Low Risk, Medium ROI)\n- Option 2: Strategic Partnership (Medium Risk, High ROI)\n- Option 3: In-house Development (High Risk, High ROI)\nRecommendation: Quick Implementation for immediate results.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nOption A (Quick Implementation): Timeline - 1 month, Metrics - Increased efficiency, Risk Level - Low\nOption B (In-house Development): Timeline - 6 months, Metrics - Cost savings, Risk Level - High\nRecommendation: Option A for quicker results with lower risk.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- CEO: Increase operational efficiency through quick implementation.\n- CFO: Drive cost savings through strategic partnerships.\n- CTO: Explore potential in-house development opportunities.\n- CMO: Enhance market positioning with new implementation strategies.\n- HR Manager: Streamline processes for better employee experience.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals  \nSynergistic sub-goals:\n- Implement employee training programs for efficient adoption of new strategies (Strong synergy).\n- Improve communication channels for better alignment across teams (Weak synergy).  \n\nNext step: Proceed with the Quick Implementation strategy and monitor progress closely for maximum impact.', 0, 0, '2025-05-07 07:59:17'),
(97, '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'Can u please provide it in a more detailed verison like all the steps detaled explained', '✅ Final Outcome Summary  \n- Restate recommendation clearly with timeline & next step option:\n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \n- Acknowledge the user’s goal in a strategic, co-pilot tone. Ask if document scan is needed.  \n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \n- Summarize findings or fallback logic (state clearly if no docs are found).  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \n- Assess Complexity, Resource Requirements, Strategic Alignment.  \n- Assign Aggressiveness: Easy / Moderate / Aggressive.  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: X/10  \n- Feasibility: X/10  \n- Alignment: X/10  \n- Total Score: XX/30  \n- Interpretation: Add strengths/risks analysis.  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \n- Present 3–4 named paths with: Description, Estimated Effort, Risk, ROI Potential.  \n- Recommend one or prompt user choice.  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \n- Simulate 2 options (A & B).  \n- For each: Timeline, Metrics, Risk Level.  \n- Recommend best-fit scenario.  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- List 3–5 key roles  \n- For each: Relevance Score (if possible), Rephrased goal in their domain.\n📌 Complementary Goals  \n- Suggest 1–2 synergistic sub-goals.  \n- State synergy level: Strong / Weak / Needs Validation.  \n\nNEVER SKIP A STEP. Use fallback assumptions if real data is unavailable.  \nMirror executive tone: Clear, strategic, concise. Use emojis for section headers.', 0, 0, '2025-05-07 08:17:52'),
(98, '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year.', '✅ Final Outcome Summary \n\nRecommendation:\nBased on the assessment, I recommend pursuing the \"Empowerment and Recognition\" strategy path. This path involves implementing programs that empower and recognize the sales team, aimed at reducing voluntary turnover. The estimated effort is moderate, with low to moderate risks and high ROI potential. The next step would be to develop a detailed plan for implementing this strategy. \n\nTimeline:\n- Develop detailed plan: 1 month\n\nNext Step Option:\n- Schedule a meeting to discuss the detailed plan and allocate resources accordingly. \n\nThank you for the opportunity to assist with this goal. Please let us know if you need any further assistance.', 0, 0, '2025-05-07 18:34:53'),
