(1, '32', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'I want to enhance employee wellness this year — where do I start?', 'Enhancing employee wellness is a great goal for the year. Here are some steps you can take to get started:\n\n1. Conduct a wellness survey: Start by gathering information on the current state of employee wellness. This could include a survey to gauge interest in wellness programs, identify potential areas of improvement, and understand the needs and preferences of your employees.\n\n2. Create a wellness program: Based on the results of the survey, create a tailored wellness program that addresses the specific needs and interests of your employees. This could include physical activity challenges, mental health resources, nutrition education, stress management workshops, and more.\n\n3. Promote a culture of wellness: Encourage a healthy workplace culture by promoting wellness initiatives, providing incentives for participation, and emphasizing the importance of employee well-being. This could include offering healthy snacks in the office, hosting wellness events, and providing resources for em', '2025-04-21 13:48:38'),
