(10, '38', '4', '[{\"question_id\":\"40\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"41\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"42\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"43\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '8', '11', 'Enhance Employee Wellness”', 'Employee wellness is an increasingly important aspect of workplace culture, as it has been shown that happy and healthy employees are more productive and engaged in their work. Here are some ways to enhance employee wellness in your organization:\n\n1. Provide access to mental health resources: Offer employee assistance programs, counseling services, or mental health workshops to support employees\' mental well-being.\n\n2. Promote work-life balance: Encourage employees to take breaks, use vacation days, and unplug from work after hours to prevent burnout.\n\n3. Offer wellness incentives: Provide incentives for employees to engage in wellness activities such as gym memberships, fitness challenges, or healthy eating programs.\n\n4. Create a positive work environment: Foster a culture of respect, collaboration, and communication to promote employee well-being.\n\n5. Encourage physical activity: Provide opportunities for employees to engage in physical activity during the workday, such as walking me', '2025-04-21 18:39:56'),
