(41, '57', '21', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'I want to enhance employee wellness this year — where do I start?', 'Enhancing employee wellness is a great goal to have for your organization. Here are some steps you can take to get started:\n\n1. Conduct a wellness assessment: Before implementing any wellness initiatives, it\'s important to understand the current wellness needs and challenges of your employees. You can do this through surveys, focus groups, or interviews to gather feedback on their wellness preferences and concerns.\n\n2. Create a wellness program: Based on the results of the assessment, develop a wellness program that addresses the specific needs and interests of your employees. This could include initiatives such as fitness challenges, nutrition education, mental health resources, stress management workshops, and incentives for healthy behaviors.\n\n3. Provide resources and support: Make sure employees have access to the resources and support they need to participate in the wellness program. This could include providing healthy snacks in the office, offering wellness workshops or seminars', '2025-04-22 15:02:40'),
(42, '58', '4', '[{\"question_id\":\"30\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"31\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"32\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"33\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '5', '8', 'how to grow my business by 20%', '1. Evaluate your current business operations and identify areas for growth. This could include expanding your product or service offerings, entering new markets, or improving your marketing and sales strategies.\n\n2. Set specific and achievable goals for your business growth, such as increasing sales revenue, acquiring new customers, or expanding your online presence.\n\n3. Develop a detailed business plan outlining the steps you need to take to achieve your growth goals. This plan should include timelines, milestones, and resources needed to support your growth strategy.\n\n4. Invest in marketing and advertising efforts to reach a larger audience and attract new customers. This could include social media marketing, email campaigns, SEO, and online advertising.\n\n5. Consider expanding your business through partnerships, collaborations, or strategic alliances with other companies or organizations in your industry.\n\n6. Focus on improving customer satisfaction and retention to increase repeat b', '2025-04-22 19:05:44'),
(43, '69', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'hello', 'Hello! Thank you for sharing your goal with me. Let\'s go through the GoalSync process to help you achieve your goal.\n\nStep 1: Chat Acknowledgement\nHello! I\'m here to assist you with your goal.\n\nStep 2: Document Insights\nUnfortunately, no specific goal was mentioned in your message. \n\nStep 3: Goal Assessment Summary\nSince no specific goal was provided, we will need more information to assess and support your goal effectively.\n\nStep 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)\nWithout a clear goal, we are unable to score its impact, feasibility, and alignment at this time.\n\nStep 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)\nWe will need additional details to create a strategy map to guide you towards achieving your goal.\n\nStep 6: Scenario Simulations\nGiven the missing information, we cannot proceed with scenario simulations at this point.\n\nStep 7: Rephrased Goals by Role\nUntil we have a specific goal from you, we are unable to rephrase it based on different roles.\n\nComplementary Goals (if applicable)\n', '2025-04-24 10:53:34'),
(44, '75', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'need expense projection for upcoming month of my company ?', NULL, '2025-04-25 05:58:41'),
(45, '75', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'need expense projection for upcoming month of my company ?', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nHello, thank you for sharing your goal with me. I\'d be happy to assist you with creating an expense projection for the upcoming month of your company.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nPlease provide me with any relevant information or data you have regarding your company\'s expenses for the upcoming month.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nYour goal is to create an expense projection for the upcoming month of your company to better understand and plan for financial obligations.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \n- Impact: Creating an expense projection can greatly help in budgeting and financial planning.\n- Feasibility: Depending on the available data and resources, creating an expense projection should be feasible.\n- Alignment: Aligns well with your goal of financial management.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nWe will analyze the current expenses, trends, and factors affecting your company\'s finances to create an accurate expense projection.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nBy considering various scenarios and factors, we can simulate different outcomes to better prepare for potential financial challenges or opportunities in the upcoming month.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- CEO: Develop a clear and accurate expense projection to guide financial decision-making.\n- CFO: Analyze financial data and trends to create a detailed expense projection for the upcoming month.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \n- Implement cost-saving measures to optimize expenses.\n- Monitor and adjust the expense projection as needed throughout the month.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nThe final outcome will be a detailed and strategic expense projection for the upcoming month of your company, assisting in financial planning and decision-making.', '2025-04-25 06:39:31'),
(46, '75', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'need expense projection for upcoming month of my company ?', '🧩 Step 1: Thank you for sharing your goal of needing an expense projection for the upcoming month of your company.\n\n📁 Step 2: Noted. I will document this goal for reference and analysis.\n\n📊 Step 3: The goal is to create an expense projection for the upcoming month of the company.\n\n📈 Step 4: Let\'s assess the impact, feasibility, and alignment of this goal in relation to your company\'s overall objectives.\n\n- Impact: A well-prepared expense projection can provide valuable insights for financial planning and decision-making.\n- Feasibility: The availability of accurate financial data and resources will be crucial in achieving this goal.\n- Alignment: Ensuring that the expense projection aligns with the company\'s financial goals and targets is essential.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: We will map out strategic decision paths to create an accurate expense projection for the upcoming month.\n\n🔮 Step 6: We will simulate different scenarios to anticipate potential outcomes and adjust the expense projection accordingly.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased goal by role:\n- For the Finance Team: \"Develop a detailed expense projection for the upcoming month to guide financial planning.\"\n\n📌 Complementary Goals: Consider setting a goal to review and analyze past expense data for more accurate projections.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary: By following the GoalSync method, we aim to provide you with a comprehensive and strategic expense projection for the upcoming month of your company.', '2025-04-25 06:40:15'),
(47, '75', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"21\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"22\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"23\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"24\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '4', '6', 'need expense projection for upcoming month of my company ?', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal with me regarding the expense projection for the upcoming month of your company.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nI will start by gathering all relevant information and insights related to your company\'s expenses.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nYour goal is to have an expense projection for the upcoming month to better manage your company\'s finances.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \nTo assess this goal, we will evaluate the impact of having an accurate expense projection, the feasibility of obtaining the necessary data, and its alignment with your company\'s overall financial objectives.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nWe will create a strategy map that outlines the decision paths required to gather the necessary information and create the expense projection.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nWe will run scenario simulations based on different expense variables and factors to ensure the projection is as accurate as possible.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- CEO: To have a clear expense projection for the upcoming month to make informed financial decisions.\n- CFO: To analyze and validate the expense data for accuracy and reliability.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \nComplementary goals may include optimizing expenses, identifying cost-saving opportunities, and improving financial forecasting processes.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nThe final outcome will be a detailed expense projection for the upcoming month that will support your company in making sound financial decisions.', '2025-04-25 06:41:15'),
(50, '78', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"40\",\"answer\":\"Expand outreach to underrepresented communities, anonymized screening for select roles, and ERG-driven awareness.\"},{\"question_id\":\"41\",\"answer\":\"Inclusion is tracked through engagement pulse surveys and quarterly review of inclusive behaviors across leadership levels.\"},{\"question_id\":\"42\",\"answer\":\"Use of structured rubrics, bias interrupter prompts during interviews, and training for hiring panels.\"},{\"question_id\":\"43\",\"answer\":\"It\'s a foundational pillar \\u2014 our culture and innovation strategy both rely on a diverse, inclusive workforce.\"}]', '6', '6', '8', '11', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year.', '🧩 Step 1: Thank you for sharing your goal to reduce voluntary turnover in your sales team this year.\n\n📁 Step 2: Based on your input, it is evident that retaining your sales team members is a key priority for your organization.\n\n📊 Step 3: The goal of reducing voluntary turnover in the sales team is aimed at improving employee retention and ultimately enhancing the team\'s overall performance.\n\n📈 Step 4: In terms of impact, decreasing turnover can lead to increased team stability and productivity. Feasibility will depend on the underlying reasons for turnover, while alignment with the organization\'s objectives is crucial.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Developing strategies such as implementing mentorship programs, improving compensation and benefits, and enhancing career development opportunities can help address turnover issues. Decision paths may include conducting exit interviews to gather insights and implementing targeted retention initiatives.\n\n🔮 Step 6: By simulating scenarios where these strategies are implemented, we can assess their potential effectiveness in reducing voluntary turnover within the sales team.\n\n👥 Step 7: The rephrased goals by role could be:\n- Sales Manager: Ensure proper onboarding and provide continuous support to sales team members to reduce turnover.\n- HR Manager: Implement retention strategies and conduct regular feedback sessions to address turnover issues.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable): Enhancing communication channels within the sales team to foster a positive work environment.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary: By strategically implementing retention strategies and addressing underlying issues, we aim to reduce voluntary turnover in the sales team, leading to enhanced team performance and organization success.', '2025-04-25 15:30:45'),
(51, '78', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"40\",\"answer\":\"Expand outreach to underrepresented communities, anonymized screening for select roles, and ERG-driven awareness.\"},{\"question_id\":\"41\",\"answer\":\"Inclusion is tracked through engagement pulse surveys and quarterly review of inclusive behaviors across leadership levels.\"},{\"question_id\":\"42\",\"answer\":\"Use of structured rubrics, bias interrupter prompts during interviews, and training for hiring panels.\"},{\"question_id\":\"43\",\"answer\":\"It\'s a foundational pillar \\u2014 our culture and innovation strategy both rely on a diverse, inclusive workforce.\"}]', '6', '6', '8', '11', 'We want to increase employee participation in learning programs by 30%', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal with us. We appreciate your focus on increasing employee participation in learning programs.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nTo better understand your objective, could you please provide insights on your current employee learning programs and the factors affecting participation rates?\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nYour goal is to increase employee participation in learning programs by 30%.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \nImpact: Increasing employee participation can lead to enhanced skills and job satisfaction.\nFeasibility: Depending on current participation rates, achieving a 30% increase may require implementing effective strategies.\nAlignment: This goal aligns with the organization\'s focus on continuous employee development.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nPossible decision paths could include enhancing program content, promoting learning opportunities, and offering incentives for participation.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nSimulations could explore the potential impact of different strategies on employee engagement and overall performance.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- HR Manager: Develop strategies to increase employee participation in learning programs by 30%.\n- Learning & Development Specialist: Enhance program content to boost employee engagement.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \nA complementary goal could focus on measuring the effectiveness of the learning programs in improving employee performance.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nBy increasing employee participation in learning programs by 30%, your organization can foster a culture of continuous learning and development.', '2025-04-25 15:35:11'),
(52, '80', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'Our goal is to boost brand recall in the US market by 10% this year', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement\nThank you for sharing your goal of boosting brand recall in the US market by 10% this year.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights\nTo effectively boost brand recall, we will need to understand the current brand perception in the US market and identify key factors that influence recall rates.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary\nThe goal to increase brand recall by 10% demonstrates a clear focus on enhancing brand visibility and recognition among the target audience in the US market.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)\nImpact: Increasing brand recall can lead to higher brand recognition and customer engagement.\nFeasibility: Achieving a 10% increase may require significant resources and strategic planning.\nAlignment: This goal aligns with the overall marketing objectives and growth targets of the organization.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)\nDeveloping a comprehensive marketing campaign, optimizing digital presence, and enhancing customer engagement strategies could be key decision paths to achieve the goal.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations\nSimulating different scenarios such as investing in targeted advertising, sponsoring events, or collaborating with influencers can help determine the most effective approach.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role\n- Marketing Team: Develop and implement a brand recall strategy to achieve a 10% increase in the US market.\n- Sales Team: Align sales efforts with marketing initiatives to support brand recall objectives.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)\nComplementary goals could include increasing customer engagement metrics, enhancing brand loyalty, and improving brand reputation in the US market.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary\nBy strategically implementing marketing initiatives and optimizing brand visibility, we aim to achieve a 10% boost in brand recall in the US market, ultimately enhancing brand recognition and driving business growth.', '2025-04-25 15:48:39'),
(53, '80', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'We need to improve lead conversion rates from our digital ads.', '🧩 Step 1: Thank you for sharing your goal to improve lead conversion rates from your digital ads.\n\n📁 Step 2: It\'s important to document that increasing lead conversion rates is a critical aspect of your marketing strategy.\n\n📊 Step 3: In assessing this goal, it is evident that enhancing lead conversion rates can lead to higher ROI and improved overall performance in your digital advertising efforts.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring - Impact: High, Feasibility: Moderate, Alignment: High\n\n🗺️ Step 5: By mapping out decision paths, we can explore strategies such as optimizing ad performance, refining targeting methods, and improving landing page design to increase lead conversion rates.\n\n🔮 Step 6: In scenario simulations, we can test different variables and analyze their impact on lead conversion rates to determine the most effective strategies.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role:\n- Marketing Team: Increase lead conversion rates by refining digital ad strategies.\n- Design Team: Enhance landing page design to improve user experience and drive conversions.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals:\n- Implementing A/B testing to optimize ad performance.\n- Utilizing retargeting strategies to re-engage potential leads.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary: By strategically focusing on improving lead conversion rates from digital ads, we aim to drive enhanced performance, increased ROI, and overall success in your marketing efforts.', '2025-04-25 15:53:32'),
(54, '83', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year.', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal to reduce voluntary turnover in the sales team this year.  \n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nVoluntary turnover in the sales team can have a significant impact on productivity and morale.  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nThe goal is clear: decrease voluntary turnover in the sales team by implementing effective retention strategies.  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \n- Impact: High\n- Feasibility: Moderate\n- Alignment: High  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nPossible strategies include improving leadership support, enhancing employee engagement, and providing career development opportunities.  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nSimulating various scenarios will help identify the most effective retention strategies for the sales team.  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- Sales Managers: Implement targeted retention initiatives\n- Sales Representatives: Engage in career development opportunities  \n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \nConsider aligning this goal with overall employee satisfaction and retention strategies.  \n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nOverall, the goal to reduce voluntary turnover in the sales team is achievable through strategic planning and collaboration among team members.', '2025-04-28 13:38:34'),
(55, '86', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'Our goal this year is to increase brand awareness in North America. Can you help me assess this and guide the team?', '🧩 **Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement**\nAbsolutely, I can assist you with assessing and guiding the team to increase brand awareness in North America this year.\n\n📁 **Step 2: Document Insights**\nTo begin, let\'s gather insights on your current brand awareness strategies in North America and any previous efforts.\n\n📊 **Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary**\nIncreasing brand awareness in North America is a crucial objective for your team this year.\n\n📈 **Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)**\nWe will evaluate the impact, feasibility, and alignment of this goal to ensure its success.\n\n🗺️ **Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)**\nWe will create decision paths to determine the most effective strategies for expanding brand awareness in North America.\n\n🔮 **Step 6: Scenario Simulations**\nWe will also run scenario simulations to anticipate potential outcomes and adjust strategies accordingly.\n\n👥 **Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role**\nFor the marketing team, the goal is to implement targeted campaigns to increase brand visibility in North America.\n\n📌 **Complementary Goals (if applicable)**\nComplementary goals may include enhancing customer engagement and driving conversions in tandem with brand awareness efforts.\n\n✅ **Final Outcome Summary**\nThe final outcome will be a strategic roadmap to elevate brand awareness in North America this year. Let\'s get started on achieving this goal!', '2025-05-02 11:44:36'),
(56, '88', '4', '[{\"question_id\":\"44\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"45\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"46\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"47\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '6', '6', '9', '12', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year.', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal of reducing voluntary turnover in your sales team this year.  \n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nVoluntary turnover can impact team morale, productivity, and overall company success.  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nYour goal to reduce voluntary turnover aligns with improving team stability and performance.  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)  \n- Impact: High\n- Feasibility: Moderate\n- Alignment: High  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)  \nPossible strategies could include enhanced employee engagement initiatives, conducting exit interviews to identify key issues, and implementing retention incentive programs.  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nSimulations could explore the effectiveness of different strategies on reducing turnover rates and retaining top sales talent.  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- Sales Team Leader: Enhance team morale and reduce turnover through targeted support and recognition programs.  \n- HR Manager: Develop retention strategies and analyze turnover data to address key issues proactively.  \n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)  \nComplementary goals could include improving onboarding processes for new hires and providing ongoing training and development opportunities.  \n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary  \nBy focusing on reducing voluntary turnover in your sales team, you can create a more stable and engaged workforce, leading to improved performance and business success.', '2025-05-02 13:29:28'),
(57, '90', '2', '[{\"question_id\":\"44\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"45\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"46\",\"answer\":\"text\"},{\"question_id\":\"47\",\"answer\":\"text\"}]', '6', '6', '9', '12', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year. GOALSYNC - GPT INSTRUCTION SET For Standardized Output Generation (1) 1.docx', '🧩 Step 1: Thank you for sharing your goal of reducing voluntary turnover in your sales team this year.\n\n📁 Step 2: Based on your goal, it is important to document insights regarding the current turnover rates, reasons for voluntary turnover, employee feedback, and historical data on turnover trends.\n\n📊 Step 3: The goal assessment summary is focused on reducing voluntary turnover within the sales team to improve employee retention and overall team stability.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring your goal based on Impact, Feasibility, and Alignment is crucial for strategic planning. This will help determine the potential impact of reducing turnover, feasibility of implementing changes, and alignment with organizational objectives.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Developing a strategy map with decision paths will involve analyzing potential interventions, such as improving retention strategies, addressing employee concerns, and enhancing the overall sales team environment.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Through scenario simulations, we can explore different outcomes based on various strategies to reduce turnover, identifying potential obstacles and solutions to achieve your goal effectively.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased goal by role: \"As the sales team leader, I aim to implement effective retention strategies to decrease voluntary turnover within the sales team this year.\"\n\n📌 Complementary Goals: Enhancing employee engagement, improving communication within the sales team, and strengthening leadership development programs may support the main goal of reducing turnover.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary: By employing a strategic approach focused on retention strategies and employee satisfaction, we aim to reduce voluntary turnover in the sales team, leading to improved team performance and overall business success.', '2025-05-02 13:55:33'),
(58, '93', '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'I need a 20% increase in my sales .', '🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement\nThank you for sharing your goal of needing a 20% increase in your sales.\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights\nDocumenting the goal of a 20% sales increase for reference.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary\nThe goal is clear - a 20% increase in sales.\n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring (Impact, Feasibility, Alignment)\nImpact: Achieving a 20% increase in sales would significantly boost revenue.\nFeasibility: Feasibility depends on current market conditions and sales strategies.\nAlignment: Sales increase aligns with business growth objectives.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map (Decision Paths)\nStrategy options may include optimizing marketing campaigns, expanding reach to new markets, or improving sales team performance.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations\nSimulating scenarios based on different strategies to achieve a 20% sales increase.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role\n- Sales Manager: Increase sales by 20% through strategic initiatives.\n- Marketing Team: Support sales growth with targeted campaigns.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals (if applicable)\nComplementary goals may focus on improving customer retention or enhancing product offerings.\n\n✅ Final Outcome Summary\nThe final outcome will be a comprehensive strategy to achieve your goal of a 20% increase in sales.', '2025-05-07 06:13:07'),
(59, '94', '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'I need a 20% increase in my sales .', '✅ Final Outcome Summary  \n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nAcknowledging the user\'s goal of a 20% increase in sales. Do you need to scan any documents for this goal?\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nNo documents found, relying on discussed information.  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nAssessing the complexity, resource requirements, and strategic alignment of the sales increase goal.  \n- Complexity: Moderate  \n- Resource Requirements: Medium  \n- Strategic Alignment: High  \n- Assign Aggressiveness: Moderate  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: 8/10  \n- Feasibility: 7/10  \n- Alignment: 9/10  \n- Total Score: 24/30  \n- Interpretation: High potential impact, moderate feasibility, strong strategic alignment but requires significant effort.  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \nPresenting 3-4 named paths with descriptions, estimated effort, risk, and ROI potential.  \nRecommendation: Focus on high-value customer retention for steady growth.  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nSimulating 2 options (A & B) with timelines, metrics, and risk levels.  \nRecommendation: Option B - Introduce targeted marketing campaigns for existing customer base.  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- Sales Manager: Increase repeat sales by developing loyalty programs.  \n- Marketing Director: Improve customer acquisition strategies to support sales growth.  \n- Financial Analyst: Monitor ROI of implemented marketing initiatives.  \n\n📌 Complementary Goals  \nSuggesting a synergistic sub-goal of improving customer satisfaction to strengthen loyalty programs.  \nSynergy Level: Strong  \n\nNext Step: Implement targeted marketing campaigns for existing customer base to increase sales.', '2025-05-07 06:19:40');
