ll required details and information are included and presented effectively.\n  \n8. **Delivery to User:**  \n   - Provide the user with the detailed format output derived from the document.\n   - Seek feedback or additional clarification if needed to meet the user\'s requirements.\n\n9. **Closure:**  \n   - Confirm with the user that the detailed format output aligns with their expectations and fulfills their request.\n   - Thank the user for their collaboration and assure them of continued support.', '2025-05-07 08:01:14'),
