(79, '97', '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'i need proper answer', '✅ **Final Outcome Summary**\n\n🧩 **Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement**  \n- Acknowledge the user’s goal in a strategic, co-pilot tone. Ask if document scan is needed.  \n\n📁 **Step 2: Document Insights**  \n- Summarize findings or fallback logic (state clearly if no docs are found).  \n\n📊 **Step 3: Goal Assessment**  \n- Assess Complexity, Resource Requirements, Strategic Alignment.  \n- Assign Aggressiveness: Easy / Moderate / Aggressive.  \n\n📈 **Step 4: Scoring**  \n- Impact: X/10  \n- Feasibility: X/10  \n- Alignment: X/10  \n- Total Score: XX/30  \n- Interpretation: Add strengths/risks analysis.  \n\n🗺️ **Step 5: Strategy Map**  \n- Present 3–4 named paths with: Description, Estimated Effort, Risk, ROI Potential.  \n- Recommend one or prompt user choice.  \n\n🔮 **Step 6: Scenario Simulations**  \n- Simulate 2 options (A & B).  \n- For each: Timeline, Metrics, Risk Level.  \n- Recommend best-fit scenario.  \n\n👥 **Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role**  \n- List 3–5 key roles  \n- For each: Relevance Score (if possible), Rephrased goal in their domain.  \n\n📌 **Complementary Goals**  \n- Suggest 1–2 synergistic sub-goals.  \n- State synergy level: Strong / Weak / Needs Validation.  ', '2025-05-07 08:19:59'),
(80, '97', '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'i need20% increase in mym sales', '✅ Final Outcome Summary  \n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal of needing a 20% increase in sales. Do you have any documents to share for more insights?\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nNo documents shared.  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \nComplexity: Moderate  \nResource Requirements: High  \nStrategic Alignment: Strong  \nAggressiveness: Aggressive  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \nImpact: 9/10  \nFeasibility: 7/10  \nAlignment: 8/10  \nTotal Score: 24/30  \nInterpretation: Strong potential for growth, but resource-intensive. Risks include potential market saturation.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \n1. Boost Marketing Efforts: High effort, Moderate Risk, High ROI Potential.  \n2. Expand Distribution Channels: Moderate effort, Moderate Risk, Moderate ROI Potential.  \n3. Develop Customer Loyalty Programs: Moderate effort, Low Risk, Moderate ROI Potential.  \nRecommendation: Boost Marketing Efforts for quick impact.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nOption A (Boost Marketing Efforts): 6 months timeline, 15% increase in sales, Moderate risk level.  \nOption B (Expand Distribution Channels): 9 months timeline, 20% increase in sales, High risk level.  \nRecommendation: Option A for quicker results with manageable risks.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n1. Sales Team: Achieve 20% increase in sales revenue by implementing new marketing strategies.  \n2. Marketing Team: Drive a 20% growth in sales through targeted campaigns and promotions.  \n3. Operations Team: Support the increase in sales by optimizing supply chain and logistics.  \n\n📌 Complementary Goals  \nSynergistic goal: Enhance customer experience to complement sales growth efforts.  \nSynergy level: Strong  \n\nNext Steps: Implement Boost Marketing Efforts strategy and monitor progress closely.', '2025-05-07 08:20:43'),
(81, '97', '17', '[{\"question_id\":\"53\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"54\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"55\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"56\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '5', '7', '10', '17', 'Can u please provide it in a more detailed verison like all the steps detaled explained', '✅ Final Outcome Summary  \n- Restate recommendation clearly with timeline & next step option:\n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \n- Acknowledge the user’s goal in a strategic, co-pilot tone. Ask if document scan is needed.  \n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \n- Summarize findings or fallback logic (state clearly if no docs are found).  \n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \n- Assess Complexity, Resource Requirements, Strategic Alignment.  \n- Assign Aggressiveness: Easy / Moderate / Aggressive.  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: X/10  \n- Feasibility: X/10  \n- Alignment: X/10  \n- Total Score: XX/30  \n- Interpretation: Add strengths/risks analysis.  \n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \n- Present 3–4 named paths with: Description, Estimated Effort, Risk, ROI Potential.  \n- Recommend one or prompt user choice.  \n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \n- Simulate 2 options (A & B).  \n- For each: Timeline, Metrics, Risk Level.  \n- Recommend best-fit scenario.  \n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n- List 3–5 key roles  \n- For each: Relevance Score (if possible), Rephrased goal in their domain.\n📌 Complementary Goals  \n- Suggest 1–2 synergistic sub-goals.  \n- State synergy level: Strong / Weak / Needs Validation.  \n\nNEVER SKIP A STEP. Use fallback assumptions if real data is unavailable.  \nMirror executive tone: Clear, strategic, concise. Use emojis for section headers.', '2025-05-07 08:21:28'),
(82, '98', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'Our goal is to boost brand recall in the US market by 10% this year', '✅ Final Recommendation Summary\n\n🧩 Step 1: Chat Acknowledgement  \nThank you for sharing your goal to boost brand recall in the US market by 10% this year. Do you require a document scan for further insights?\n\n📁 Step 2: Document Insights  \nAfter reviewing available documents, no specific data relating to brand recall in the US market was found.\n\n📊 Step 3: Goal Assessment Summary  \n- Complexity: Moderate  \n- Resource Requirements: Medium  \n- Strategic Alignment: Aligned  \n- Aggressiveness: Moderate  \n\n📈 Step 4: Scoring  \n- Impact: 8/10  \n- Feasibility: 7/10  \n- Alignment: 9/10  \n- Total Score: 24/30  \n- Strengths: Strong brand presence in the US.\n- Risks: Relying on traditional marketing methods.\n\n🗺️ Step 5: Strategy Map  \n1. Increase online presence with targeted ads\n2. Collaborate with influencers for brand endorsements\n3. Develop interactive social media campaigns\nRecommendation: Implement option 1 to boost brand recall effectively.\n\n🔮 Step 6: Scenario Simulations  \nOption A - Increase online presence: Expected timeline - 3 months, Metrics - Increase in website traffic, Risk Level - Low\nOption B - Collaborate with influencers: Expected timeline - 4 months, Metrics - Increase in social media engagement, Risk level - Moderate\nRecommendation: Option A - Increase online presence is the best-fit scenario.\n\n👥 Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role  \n1. Marketing Manager - Increase online visibility by leveraging digital platforms.\n2. Social Media Manager - Enhance brand engagement through interactive campaigns.\n3. Sales Team - Utilize brand recall to drive sales growth.\n\n📌 Complementary Goals  \n- Implement customer loyalty programs to strengthen brand recall.\n- Synergy Level: Strong. \n\nNext Step: Begin implementation of the online presence strategy and monitor metrics for effectiveness.', '2025-05-07 18:35:11'),
