\n- Sales Team: Improve follow-up processes to capitalize on increased leads.  \n📌 Complementary Goals  \n- Develop personalized lead nurturing content to strengthen customer relationships. Suggested synergy level: Strong.  \n\nRemember to share the detailed action plan for Path 2 implementation with the user for approval.', '2025-05-07 18:36:39'),
(84, '98', '20', '[{\"question_id\":\"69\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"70\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"71\",\"answer\":\"test\"},{\"question_id\":\"72\",\"answer\":\"test\"}]', '3', '9', '14', '21', 'I want to reduce voluntary turnover in our sales team this year.', '✅ Final Outcome Summary \n\nRecommendation:\nBased on the assessment, I recommend pursuing the \"Empowerment and Recognition\" strategy path. This path involves implementing programs that empower and recognize the sales team, aimed at reducing voluntary turnover. The estimated effort is moderate, with low to moderate risks and high ROI potential. The next step would be to develop a detailed plan for implementing this strategy. \n\nTimeline:\n- Develop detailed plan: 1 month\n\nNext Step Option:\n- Schedule a meeting to discuss the detailed plan and allocate resources accordingly. \n\nThank you for the opportunity to assist with this goal. Please let us know if you need any further assistance.', '2025-05-07 18:37:19');
