tion**: Focus on Product Diversification, balancing effort and potential ROI.\n\n🔮 **Step 6: Scenario Simulations**  \n- **Option A: Market Expansion**  \n  - **Timeline**: 9-12 months  \n  - **Metrics**: Revenue growth, Market share increase  \n  - **Risk Level**: High  \n- **Option B: Product Diversification**  \n  - **Timeline**: 6-9 months  \n  - **Metrics**: Revenue growth, Customer acquisition  \n  - **Risk Level**: Medium  \n\n**Best-fit Scenario**: Option B - Product Diversification\n\n👥 **Step 7: Rephrased Goals by Role**  \n1. **Sales Manager**  \n   - **Relevance Score**: 9/10  \n   - **Rephrased Goal**: \"Increase sales volume by 20% through new product lines.\"\n   \n2. **Marketing Director**  \n   - **Relevance Score**: 8/10  \n   - **Rephrased Goal**: \"Expand market reach by 15% targeting new demographics.\"\n\n3. **Operations Manager**  \n   - **Relevance Score**: 7/10  \n   - **Rephrased Goal**: \"Enhance production efficiency to support revenue growth.\"\n\n📌 **Complementary Goals**  \n1. **Enhance Digital Marketing Strategy**  \n   - **Synergy Level**: Strong  \n2. **Strengthen Customer Retention Programs**  \n   - **Synergy Level**: Needs Validation  \n\nThis structured approach ensures alignment with strategic objectives while balancing potential risks and rewards.', '2025-05-29 05:42:04');
