(300, '298', '41', '[{\"question_id\":\"99\",\"answer\":\"Curiosity\\r\\n\\r\\nCraftsmanship\\r\\n\\r\\nCustomer Obsession\\r\\n\\r\\nOwnership\\r\\n(These values guided us when we were a 5-person startup \\u2014 we still hire and promote based on them.)\"},{\"question_id\":\"100\",\"answer\":\"Yes \\u2014 we have a culture deck and onboarding playbook that captures our origin story, core beliefs, and how we made decisions early on. But only a few teams refer to it actively now.\"},{\"question_id\":\"101\",\"answer\":\"Ownership. I want everyone \\u2014 regardless of level \\u2014 to take initiative like they\\u2019re running the company.\"},{\"question_id\":\"102\",\"answer\":\"We\\u2019re hiring 8\\u201310 people per month across Tech, Customer Ops, and Sales. That\\u2019s over 35% growth expected this year.\"},{\"question_id\":\"103\",\"answer\":\"Not officially. Our People & Culture team tries to hold the line, but we don\\u2019t have embedded culture leads within each department.\"}]', '5', '17', '24', '33', 'LinkedIn Name First Name Last Name Position / Role in the company Job Function Organisation ID Location Industry Current Role(s) Seniority Job Function Past Role(s) Education Tenure at Company Tenure in Role Name Resolved? Profile Link Sales Navigator Profile Link About Shared Connections Shared Connection Names Linkedin Name1 FirstName1 LastName1 GM-Human Resources at HXD Solutions Group | Talent Development, Performance Acceleration engineering_technical_scientific Organization1 Hyderabad engineering_technical_scientific https://www.linkedin.com/in/ajaychandra https://www.linkedin.com/sales/lead/ACoAAABQPSoB7XWCG83OYJw4IoBuVvfaxdO3ch0,NAME_SEARCH,undefined Linkedin Name2 FirstName2 LastName2 Senior Telecom Engineer at HXD Solutions Group engineering_technical_scientific Organization1 Warangal engineering_technical_scientific https://www.linkedin.com/in/dhara-dhanunjay-85505b384 https://www.linkedin.com/sales/lead/ACoAAF6xJAEBxfVESGpvFyTbBShBtVX5ilbrits,N